{"tid":1070660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！！！！！7仔有連登AC賣","createTime":"2019-03-20T23:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T00:26:23.000Z","uid":199237,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"957e857f76aa7d499ab772ab9a42662c3b27a620","tid":1070660,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:02:43.000Z","msg":"本身小弟係有個ac嘅 <br />\n不過一個點夠我偷偷上開post上成人台個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（朋友知我ac）<br />\n所以成日心思思想開多個ac <br />\n之前連登卡出左一排又停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到三月尾又出翻！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻狗衝去7仔買左 終於開到多個ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢事你地話我昆人 比埋圖你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（卡）<br />\n<br />\n（成功開通左）<br />\n<br />\n教學如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚益cdrom 00後狗<br />\n[membre]<br />\n首先 去7仔同ok講句連登卡一張 廿蚊個款 然後比錢就ok 因為今次活動都比較內部 <br />\n可能新嚟嘅店員會唔明你講咩 呢個時候你只要講呢個驗證碼:UDx54H 比店員知 <br />\n佢就明你要買邊隻卡 咁佢都係唔明你就當場屌7佢/揾過第二間啦😪<br />\n<br />\n最後提下大家 個活動好似4月1日 24:00就會停售 想要就快d去買啦 數量有限嫁 我買完先敢分享比你地知 廢事你地一窩峰搶走曬d卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你無買到就要好似我咁等多一年先買番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/nember]"},{"pid":"66e02281beec4c0830394bed6a97186e46235cc9","tid":1070660,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:08:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32f4572e8c497d99f7f8b88abd26d18d5bda4ff5","tid":1070660,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:08:41.000Z","msg":"無加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d267de0002504e4a4a72c36f75e98ecbb752e","tid":1070660,"uid":172154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:09:14.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"7fb25a2bf5c2ae41086901e4c7767ffbfe7c4820","tid":1070660,"uid":214243,